These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, photographer, writer
1. the photographer is on the far left##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | photographer | writer | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, bartender, accountant
1. the accountant is on the far right##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | freelancer | bartender | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | board-games | card-games | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, mexican, australian
