.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, van
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | van | skateboard | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy | zombie |

